---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Terms and conditions under which football assessments and consultancy services are provided."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="legal">
        <p class="legal__intro">
          These Terms of Service outline the conditions under which football
          assessments and consultancy services are provided.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Services Provided</h2>
        <p>
          I provide independent football assessments, reports, consultations and
          development guidance based on match video or in-person observation.
        </p>

        <h2>2. Client Responsibility</h2>
        <p>Clients must ensure:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Match footage is clear and usable</li>
          <li>Information provided is accurate</li>
          <li>Any requested materials are supplied on time</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Payment</h2>
        <p>
          Payments must be made in full before assessments or consultations are
          delivered. Prices may vary by region. Refunds are not available once
          analysis has begun.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Delivery of Reports</h2>
        <p>
          Reports are delivered digitally. Delivery times may vary depending on
          video quality, availability and workload.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Use of Reports</h2>
        <p>
          Reports are for personal or internal use only and must not be
          distributed, published or used commercially without permission.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Limitation of Advice</h2>
        <p>
          All assessments represent professional opinion based on available
          information. No outcomes, selections or offers from third-party
          organisations are guaranteed.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Data Protection</h2>
        <p>
          Any personal data provided is handled in accordance with the
          <a href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Contact Information</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about these terms, please contact:
          <a href="mailto:michael@mulhernfc.com">michael@mulhernfc.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem 2rem;
    background-color: var(--color-off-white);
  }

  .legal {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .legal__intro {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--color-grey-600);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .legal h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .legal h2:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .legal p {
    color: var(--color-grey-600);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .legal a {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .legal a:hover {
    color: var(--color-gold-hover);
  }

  .legal ul {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .legal li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
    color: var(--color-grey-600);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  .legal li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.6em;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--color-gold);
  }
</style>
